    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at level 1 per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within the accepted uncertainty tolerance and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. Note: this package conforms to the Minimal profile; the digital signature is pending completion of the organizational signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
